commentTextItems.html: full outside the off stump, crashed it in the air wide of diving Duffin to extra-cover fence, finishes off in style

commentPostTextItems.html: The Players shake hands, wonderful win for Bangladesh, they win by 8 wickets. Wonderful knock from Nafees, who became the highest scorer in ODI's for Bangladesh. Zimbabwe had already sealed the series in the previous match. They win the series 3-2

commentTextItems.html: oversteps, Nafees drives to the off side
digs it out to the on side
works straight to square leg fielder
driven on the up in the gap to extra-cover fence, good shot that from Nafees
short ball outside the off stump, opens the face off the bat and runs it down to thirdman for a single
